


       
      This was a highly imaginative and very entertaining movie.  Becca and I both really enjoyed it.  Seeing it on the IMAX made it that much better.  J.K. Rowling has a great imagination; I only wonder how they are going to keep the same kid playing Harry potter after the 90 movies are made.  Despite the bad reviews I heard that it got, I thought it was very good.
     

    
